  Locus:
    Page: 171
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Freedom
---
Do you think you are not free? You are free, but you do not know that you are
free -- and it is your not knowing that you are free that is your limitation
and your imprisonment. Realize your freedom and you are free.
